data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3BR, 2 bath jewel located minutes from Camp Lejeune.  Just a short drive to park inside your two car garage.  Enjoy the ever-changing NC weather while sitting on your covered porch or step inside to this spacious living room to watch the game.  The refrigerator stays to match the other black kitchen appliances.  The backyard is waiting for lots of fun and games.  The primary bedroom features the trey ceiling and a walk-in closet along with double sinks in the bathroom.  Come on down the cul-de-sac and take a look at this cozy place to call HOME!
